translation: Make your way through this toxic forest.{#Name="説明文"}
source: Make your way through this toxic forest.{#Name="説明文"}

translation: Defeat the Trolls!{#Name="説明文"}
source: Defeat the Trolls!{#Name="説明文"}

translation: Defeat the Arch Titan!{#Name="説明文"}
source: Defeat the Arch Titan!{#Name="説明文"}

translation: Defeat the Centaur!{#Name="説明文"}
source: Defeat the Centaur!{#Name="説明文"}

translation: （リザーブ）{#Name="（リザーブ）"}
source: （リザーブ）{#Name="（リザーブ）"}

translation: （リザーブ）{#Name="（リザーブ）"}
source: （リザーブ）{#Name="（リザーブ）"}

translation: （リザーブ）{#Name="（リザーブ）"}
source: （リザーブ）{#Name="（リザーブ）"}

translation: （リザーブ）{#Name="（リザーブ）"}
source: （リザーブ）{#Name="（リザーブ）"}

translation: （リザーブ）{#Name="（リザーブ）"}
source: （リザーブ）{#Name="（リザーブ）"}

translation: （リザーブ）{#Name="（リザーブ）"}
source: （リザーブ）{#Name="（リザーブ）"}

translation: Well, this is odd.{#Name="Octa"}
source: Well, this is odd.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: What?{#Name="Zero"}
source: What?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: There are supposed to be faeries in this area.{#Name="Octa"}
source: There are supposed to be faeries in this area.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: I don't see anything.{#Name="Zero"}
source: I don't see anything.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Ah HA! See? The poison gas has killed every last—{#Name="Cent"}
source: Ah HA! See? The poison gas has killed every last—{#Name="Cent"}

translation: Please shut up.{#Name="Dito"}
source: Please shut up.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Good heavens. Are those trolls?{#Name="Octa"}
source: Good heavens. Are those trolls?{#Name="Octa"}

translation: Ugh. Trolls. Ugly, smelly, and dumb...{LF}They deserve to die.{#Name="Dito"}
source: Ugh. Trolls. Ugly, smelly, and dumb...{LF}They deserve to die.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: That's rather judgmental of you.{#Name="Decadus"}
source: That's rather judgmental of you.{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: You're damn right it's judgmental!{#Name="Dito"}
source: You're damn right it's judgmental!{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Hell, we're doing these jackasses{LF}a FAVOR by killing 'em!{#Name="Dito"}
source: Hell, we're doing these jackasses{LF}a FAVOR by killing 'em!{#Name="Dito"}

translation: I mean, it's not like they're gonna do{LF}anything worthwhile with their lives.{#Name="Dito"}
source: I mean, it's not like they're gonna do{LF}anything worthwhile with their lives.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Trust me. They'll be much happier{LF}once they're dead.{#Name="Dito"}
source: Trust me. They'll be much happier{LF}once they're dead.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: I wonder what Lady Three was{LF}trying to tell us earlier.{#Name="Decadus"}
source: I wonder what Lady Three was{LF}trying to tell us earlier.{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: She said Lady One is in this forest, yes?{#Name="Decadus"}
source: She said Lady One is in this forest, yes?{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: And that she holds a secret of some sort?{#Name="Decadus"}
source: And that she holds a secret of some sort?{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: The mysteries multiply amongst themselves...{#Name="Decadus"}
source: The mysteries multiply amongst themselves...{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: I, too, have been considering{LF}this question at some length.{#Name="Octa"}
source: I, too, have been considering{LF}this question at some length.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: But alas, whenever I think of Lady Three,{LF}my mind is distracted by non-stop images{LF}of our epic late-night fleshmongering...{#Name="Octa"}
source: But alas, whenever I think of Lady Three,{LF}my mind is distracted by non-stop images{LF}of our epic late-night fleshmongering...{#Name="Octa"}

translation: You aren't even trying, are you?{#Name="Zero"}
source: You aren't even trying, are you?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Lady Zero, look out!{#Name="Decadus"}
source: Lady Zero, look out!{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: A titan? Here? That's a bit...unexpected.{#Name="Cent"}
source: A titan? Here? That's a bit...unexpected.{#Name="Cent"}

translation: What did you do to deserve such punishment, eh?{#Name="Cent"}
source: What did you do to deserve such punishment, eh?{#Name="Cent"}

translation: 'Cause I know I didn't do anything,{LF}so it must have been you.{#Name="Cent"}
source: 'Cause I know I didn't do anything,{LF}so it must have been you.{#Name="Cent"}

translation: Quit whining and do your damn job!{#Name="Zero"}
source: Quit whining and do your damn job!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Oh, come on. Now it's a centaur?{#Name="Dito"}
source: Oh, come on. Now it's a centaur?{#Name="Dito"}

translation: What is this, a goddamn monster amusement park!?{#Name="Dito"}
source: What is this, a goddamn monster amusement park!?{#Name="Dito"}

translation: The beasts of this forest have{LF}changed, to be sure...{#Name="Octa"}
source: The beasts of this forest have{LF}changed, to be sure...{#Name="Octa"}

translation: We'd best track down Lady One with all haste.{#Name="Octa"}
source: We'd best track down Lady One with all haste.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: Agreed.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Agreed.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: But first we kill my pretty pony here.{LF}Then we can go find One.{#Name="Zero"}
source: But first we kill my pretty pony here.{LF}Then we can go find One.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Here they come!{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: Here they come!{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: We have to stop them here!{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: We have to stop them here!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: What're we gonna do!? More and more of us are falling ill!{#Name="Soldier C"}
source: What're we gonna do!? More and more of us are falling ill!{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: Yeah, well that illness won't mean shit if they get past us here!{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: Yeah, well that illness won't mean shit if they get past us here!{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: Where'd Lady Three go?{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: Where'd Lady Three go?{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: Back into the forest!{#Name="Soldier C"}
source: Back into the forest!{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: If only Lady Three were here with us!{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: If only Lady Three were here with us!{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: Dammit! Wh-What the hell is happening!?{#Name="Soldier C"}
source: Dammit! Wh-What the hell is happening!?{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: Is this fog the will of Lady Three?{#Name="Soldier F"}
source: Is this fog the will of Lady Three?{#Name="Soldier F"}

translation: Nnngh...{#Name="Soldier C"}
source: Nnngh...{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: This is an ill mist. Try not to breathe too deeply!{#Name="Soldier D"}
source: This is an ill mist. Try not to breathe too deeply!{#Name="Soldier D"}

translation: *Huff, huff...* D-Dammit... I can't breathe...{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: *Huff, huff...* D-Dammit... I can't breathe...{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: If she's made it this far, our front line must have been annihilated!{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: If she's made it this far, our front line must have been annihilated!{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: Don't think about that right now!{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: Don't think about that right now!{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: The hell is up with this forest...?{#Name="Zero"}
source: The hell is up with this forest...?{#Name="Zero"}
